Feature: User manages expenses
  Scenario: User adds a new expense
    Given I go to the new expense page
    And I fill in "Amount" with "4.50"
    And I fill in "Description" with "Part for Lawn Mower"
    And I fill in "Type" with "Equipment"
    And I fill in "Date" with "03/01/2014"
    When I press "Create"
    Then I should be on the expense list page
    And I should see "Part for Lawn Mower"
